# Portfolio Projet Master

Minimal Next.js initialization for the personal fullstack application that will combine a private project management dashboard and a public recruiter-facing portfolio.

## Initialization Commands

```bash
npx create-next-app@latest portfolio-projet-master \
  --ts \
  --tailwind \
  --eslint \
  --app \
  --use-npm \
  --import-alias "@/*" \
  --empty

cd portfolio-projet-master
npm run dev
```

The current setup was generated from the official `create-next-app` CLI and then adjusted into a cleaner project structure for future tickets.

## Available Scripts

```bash
npm run dev
npm run build
npm run start
npm run lint
```

